类 ReversiModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • ReversiModel
  • public class ReversiModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class ReversiModel is use to store the data and serve as the core of the program. It provide important information for the viewer and controller. Based on the MVC, it is less complicate than the controller because its task is very simple. Store the data.
